In [53]:
def proceso( image , G , sigma = 2.5 , b = 0.7  , cut = 1000 ):
    Dimage =skimage.filters.gaussian( image, sigma=(sigma, sigma), truncate=3.5, multichannel=True )  
    PDimage = potencial2D( Dimage )
    Fimage =  np.exp( -b*PDimage) 
    Timage = solve_Eikonal( Fimage , Gamma = G , Delta = 1 , cutOff = cut )
    B1image = Band_Propagation( Timage.copy() , P = PDimage.copy() , 
                     a = 100 , b = 1000 , Deltat = 0.0001 , Deltax = 1 , 
                     steps = 100 , beta = -0.1 , eps = 0.25 , c = 100)
    B2image = Band_Propagation( Timage.copy() , P = PDimage.copy() , 
                     a = 200 , b = 1000 , Deltat = 0.0001 , Deltax = 1 , 
                     steps = 100 , beta = 0.5 , eps = 0.5 , c = 100)
    
    fig , ax = plt.subplots( 1 , 2 )
    ax[0].imshow( image , cmap = "gray")
    ax[0].plot( G.transpose()[1] , G.transpose()[0] , "ro" ,markersize = 2)
    ax[0].axis("off")
    ax[1].imshow( image , cmap = "gray")
    ax[1].contourf( B2image , alpha = 0.7 , levels=[0,250], cmap = 'Reds')
    ax[1].axis("off")
    plt.show()

def ver( image , G ):
    plt.imshow( image , cmap = "gray")
    plt.plot( G.transpose()[1] , G.transpose()[0] , "ro" ,markersize = 2)
    plt.show()
